;SHEET
IN SHEET S2 THE REGULAR HYDROGEN BONDING PATTERN IS
DISRUPTED BY A THREE RESIDUE BULGE (RESIDUES 194 -196) IN
STRAND 2.  IN SHEET S1 A BETA BULGE IS FOUND IN STRAND 1
AT RESIDUE 64.
;
